; Coverage for op.cc lines 775-798:
; Expression error context printing for O_LAMBDA and O_CALL nodes.
; A lambda that divides by zero triggers error context printing that
; exercises the print function for these operator types.
; Also covers op.cc line 520-522 (function call error rethrow).

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test eval "(x -> x / 0)(5)" -> 1
__ERROR__
While evaluating value expression:
  (x -> (x / 0))(5)
        ^^^^^^^
While calling function '<value expr> 5':
Error: Divide by zero
end test
